[docs]    def AAPL(self):
        """
        AAPL Stock (Contract)
        :return:
        """
        contract = Contract()
        contract.symbol = "AAPL"
        contract.security_type = "STK"
        contract.currency = "USD"
        #In the API side, NASDAQ is always defined as ISLAND in the exchange field
        contract.exchange = "ISLAND"
        #! [stkcontract]
        return contract

[docs]    def stocks(self):
        stocks = [self.AAPL(), self.AXP(),self.BA(), self.CAT(), self.CSCO(), self.CVX(), self.DIS(), self.DWDP(), self.GS(),
                  self.HD(), self.IBM(), self.INTC(), self.JNJ(), self.JPM(), self.KO(), self.MCD(), self.MMM(), self.MRK(),
                  self.MSFT(), self.NKE(), self.PFE(), self.PG(), self.TRV(), self.UNH(), self.UTX(), self.V(), self.VZ(),
                  self.WBA(), self.WMT(), self.XOM()]
        yield from stocks
